column168: Was in witness protection program during final killing

column90: Coeuret, Adam aka Lesage; Guibourg, Etienne aka Abbe
column168:
Part of the Affaire des Poisons.   
Victim count: Most sources say she killed 2500 but there are some reports that have a death count of 1500, 2000, 2750 and 3000.   
Torture: tortured by way of poison.    
Confession: Confessed under torture.    
Death: Was killed on the 20th, 22nd or 23rd. Burned at the stake.
Chief Inspector at the time of the killings
